data.description: Welcome to 8005 Arezzo Dr. in the lovely Siena subdivision! This meticulously maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home was built in 2015. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting open floorplan that seamlessly connects the kitchen, living room, and dining room. The kitchen features granite countertops, an abundance of cabinets for all your storage needs, stainless steel appliances and recessed lighting. The heart of the home, the living room, is designed for relaxation and entertainment. Whether you're unwinding after a long day or enjoying a cozy movie night, this space offers comfort and versatility. Prepare to be impressed by the extremely spacious primary bedroom, a true sanctuary within the home, and boasts a generous walk-in closet. The primary bathroom is a luxurious retreat, offering a walk-in shower and a soothing soaking tub, providing the perfect spot for relaxation and self-care. The additional bedrooms are equally impressive, offering ample space for family members or guests. Whether you need a home office, a guest room, or a playroom, these rooms provide endless possibilities. Outside, you'll discover a spacious backyard, complete with a covered patio. Perfect for hosting barbecues, parties or simply enjoying the fresh air and sunshine. It's a blank canvas awaiting your personal touch and gardening aspirations. This beautiful home in Siena offers a perfect blend of modern amenities and timeless elegance. Don't miss the opportunity to make it your own! Ask your agent about the assumable loan on this property to save on your interest rate or the 2-1 buy down of your interest rate to 5.75%!
